    "author": "lordvicky",
    "description": "Per-Expeditioner free-aim feels: Gustave's crisp pistol wall, Lune's soft magic ramp, Maelle's snappy duelist click, Sciel's deep heavy wall, Verso's semi-auto buzz, Monoco's growling ramp — plus a zero-resistance Exploration state so holding R2 to sprint never fatigues. Hold Triangle + flick the left stick to pick a state; Create + D-pad jumps to Exploration/Gustave/Lune/Maelle."
